    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--padding gem-c-heading--margin-bottom-2  ">Featured</h2>

    </div>
  </div>


    <div class="grid-row">
        <div class="column-one-third">
            <div class="gem-c-image-card  brand--cabinet-office">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="The role of the analyst" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/63593/s465_agenda-analysis-business-990818.jpg"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2018-06-19">19 June 2018</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>News story</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/news/the-analysis-function">The Analysis Function</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>Introducing the Analysis Function Strategy, our vision is to integrate analysis into decision making and delivery to help improve outcomes.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>

        </div>
        <div class="column-one-third">
            <div class="gem-c-image-card  brand--cabinet-office">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="government-social-research-logo" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/61567/s465_gsr2.jpg"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2014-08-14">14 August 2014</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>Corporate information</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/organisations/civil-service-government-social-research-profession/about">About us</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>The Government Social Research profession supports the development, implementation, review and evaluation of government policy.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>

        </div>
        <div class="column-one-third">
            <div class="gem-c-image-card  brand--cabinet-office">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="civil-service-fast-stream-logo" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/61572/s465_fast-stream.png"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2018-11-07"> 7 November 2018</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>Guidance</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/publications/2017-government-social-research-service-fast-stream-scheme">Government Social Research Service Fast Stream Scheme</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>Fast Stream Social Researcher appointments are at graduate entry level or for those with less than 3 years work experience as a professional social researcher.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-row">
        <div class="column-one-third">
            <div class="gem-c-image-card  brand--cabinet-office">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="gsr-logo" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/61576/s465_gsr2.jpg"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2018-11-26">26 November 2018</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>Guidance</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/publications/how-to-apply-for-a-government-social-research-summer-student-placement">How to apply for a Government Social Research summer placement</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>This scheme is only open to applicants in their penultimate year of a social science related undergraduate degree with a substantial social research methods component.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>

        </div>
        <div class="column-one-third">
            <div class="gem-c-image-card  brand--cabinet-office">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="gsr-logo" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/61574/s465_gsr2.jpg"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2018-10-24">24 October 2018</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>Guidance</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/publications/how-to-apply-for-a-government-social-research-sandwich-student-placement">How to apply for a Government Social Research sandwich student placement</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>This scheme is only open to applicants in their penultimate year (i.e. year before the final year of study) of a social science related undergraduate degree with a substantial social research methods component.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>

        </div>
        <div class="column-one-third">
            <div class="gem-c-image-card  brand--cabinet-office">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="strategy-image" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/61568/s465_strategy.jpg"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2015-09-07"> 7 September 2015</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>Corporate report</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/publications/government-social-research-profession-strategy-2015-to-2020">Government Social Research: Profession strategy 2015 to 2020</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>How the Government Social Research (GSR) Profession will support its members over the next 5 years.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>

